 model is applicable to different\nnucleation processes and our experimental method opens the door to study the\nstructure and dynamics of materials with 4D atomic resolution.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 27 Jul 2018 16:19:53 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 20 Nov 2018 16:46:29 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 28 Feb 2019 18:22:03 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-03-01"}
