7 to 81 days. The phase\ncoverage that we achieved with ASTEP South is exceptional for a ground-based\ninstrument and the data quality enables the detection and study of variable\nobjects. These results demonstrate the high quality of Dome C for photometry in\nthe visible and for time series observations in general.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 27 Jul 2018 19:18:40 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 15 Aug 2018 19:39:26 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 9 Oct 2018 13:34:10 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Wed, 19 Dec 2018 11:06:28 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-12-20"}
